{"tid":1430613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推到全香港都要睇到 8月要搞多次百萬人遊行","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:12:52.000Z","uid":31631,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe3df5629683280e01ed8eb2f3bd4a45bc81ba4","tid":1430613,"uid":31631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:20:01.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月黎各位手足都辛苦了<br />\n<br />\n係時候搞返場百萬人遊行<br />\n聚返成個民心 再一次展示比呢個政權知道<br />\n我地對 五大訴求 缺一不可 既決心<br />\n<br />\n真係好希望大家可以再一次走上街<br />\n好清楚大家已經被無力感所籠罩住<br />\n<br />\n但我地唔可以就咁就認輸<br />\n<br />\n希望推到民陣或者其他有係呢兩個月黎有搞遊行集會既人睇到<br />\n<br />\n認同既幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1e190d7a139002bdca4ff6b5da2c2e6940f1c00","tid":1430613,"uid":31631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31916065cf330d7aca1d15b43c398a4a0273e2fe","tid":1430613,"uid":50211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:21:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a79d487c42553b856efe31555f608834f2f94a58","tid":1430613,"uid":31631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30e571a9e1f812643b5688a4fa287579675e3ef","tid":1430613,"uid":264429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"想行邊"},{"pid":"c014888f0503e8204492c50176709f35d1939ed2","tid":1430613,"uid":31631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a30e571a9e1f812643b5688a4fa287579675e3ef","tid":1430613,"uid":264429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":